com.tlabs.rootvole

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tlabs.rootvole.Entity

  • public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    An entity is a single value that might be present or not, could be several words, e.g. "alpha romeo". Can be matched by a vocabulary
